Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.Browser.findText(SearchParams)
    Consider using the non-blocking Browser.findText(SearchParams, SearchResultCallback) method
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.Browser.getAcceptLanguage()
    use BrowserContext.getAcceptLanguage() instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events.StartLoadingEvent.getFrameId() 
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BeforeSendHeadersParams.getHeaders()
    use BeforeSendHeadersParams.getHeadersEx() instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BeforeSendProxyHeadersParams.getHeaders()
    use BeforeSendProxyHeadersParams.getHeadersEx() instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.HeadersReceivedParams.getHeaders()
    use HeadersReceivedParams.getHeadersEx() instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.SendHeadersParams.getHeaders()
    use SendHeadersParams.getHeadersEx() instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.isAllowDisplayingInsecureContent()
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.isUnifiedTextcheckerEnabled()
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.isWebAudioEnabled()
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.Browser.setAcceptLanguage(String)
    the acceptLanguage parameter doesn't support the RFC 7231 Standard. Use BrowserContext.setAcceptLanguage(String) instead.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.setAllowDisplayingInsecureContent(boolean)
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.setDefaultEncoding(String)
    This method does nothing. Chromium auto-detects encoding and ignores encoding settings since version 55.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.setJavaScriptCanOpenWindowsAutomatically(boolean)
    This method does nothing. Chromium does not rely on this setting when blocking popups since version 60. For actual popup blocking see Browser.setPopupHandler(PopupHandler)}.
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.setUnifiedTextcheckerEnabled(boolean)
    com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserPreferences.setWebAudioEnabled(boolean)
